<page>
    <topic>AppendCookie Method</topic>
    <description>Adds a cookie to the response's cookie collection.</description>
    <syntax>Context.Response.AppendCookie as V (Cookie as System::Web::HttpCookie)</syntax>
    <arguments>
        <argument>
            <name>V</name>
            <description>Return type.</description>
        </argument>
        <argument>
            <name>Cookie as [System::Web::HttpCookie]</name>
            <description>The cookie to add.</description>
        </argument>
    </arguments>
    <discussion>*[xb:Context.Response.AppendCookie(Cookie)]* adds a cookie to the response's cookie collection.</discussion>
    <example><![CDATA[dim newCookie as System::Web::HttpCookie = new System::Web::HttpCookie(cookieName)
newCookie.HttpOnly = .t.
newCookie.Value = "This is the cookie's value."
Context.Response.AppendCookie(newCookie)]]></example>
